title: Brendan Sagalow: Long Island Trash
description: Comedian and podcaster Brendan Sagalow joins us and....Oh my god is traaaaash. We talk his crazy family, his teenage band, having every meal delivered, and having parents with a little bit of caaassshhh.  PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/AreYouGarbage Follow Kevin: https://www.instagram.com/kevinryancomedy/ Follow Foley: https://www.instagram.com/foleygrams/ Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the the test. Steal shampoo from hotels? Own a George Forman Grill? Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
